over your heart and taking

241
00:34:04.082 --> 00:34:09.350
three nice, deep breaths
into your heart, sending

242
00:34:09.362 --> 00:34:13.430
love and gratitude back
into yourself for showing

243
00:34:13.442 --> 00:34:16.799
up for this practice today.

244
00:34:44.270 --> 00:34:47.731
And from here, you can
stay sitting, continuing

245
00:34:47.742 --> 00:34:52.189
in your meditation for
as long as you desire.

246
00:34:52.219 --> 00:34:56.470
You can also lay down on
the floor and continue your

247
00:34:56.482 --> 00:35:00.299
integration laying down.

248
00:35:02.500 --> 00:35:06.070
And then when you're ready
to come out of your practice,

249
00:35:06.082 --> 00:35:10.670
gently, slowly allowing
yourself to bridge back

250
00:35:10.682 --> 00:35:14.871
out into awareness of your
space while maintaining

251
00:35:14.882 --> 00:35:18.699
deep presence with
your feeling body.

